						 <p>I had to downvote because of the rampant grammar mistakes. However, a cheese grater that can grate literally anything does have potential (it could certainly be turned into an AO, at least) and could lead to some interesting cross-tests. Put this through SPaG checks and flesh out the idea a bit more, and you could have something special.</p> 
