				<pubDate>Fri, 08 Jan 2021 14:22:31 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>cloud silver</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>7139802</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>IMO the test logs could be expanded, personally I don’t think the SCP being able to grate iron is a good indicator of its grating abilities.</p> <p>Also</p> <blockquote> <p>due to several incidents of misuse</p> </blockquote> <p>This could be mentioned/explained in the description or some kind of incident log, like if there’s some kind of memetic compulsion, or if it’s just some researcher taking it for personal use, etc. I feel like I saw this line and it’s just&#8230; there, there’s nothing that leads me to understand why it was being misused.</p> <p>And yeah as others mentioned, a discovery log would help too&#8230; overall, it felt kind of incomplete?</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
